{"tid":2372730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地增88宗本土病例北京佔7宗　大興區加強疫情防控","createTime":"2021-01-20T02:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T10:59:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"279d7222d5765f2da32d5cae0bd38ea60f7dd675","tid":2372730,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571331-20210120.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571331-20210120.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmegOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=9d4c75f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571331-20210120.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=97fbb08f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571331-20210120.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n內地過去一日新增103宗新型肺炎確診病例，88宗是本土病例，其中吉林有46人確診，河北19人感染，北京亦新增7宗個案。<br />\n<br />\n北京的新增病例大部分來自大興區，當地超過60萬人接受採樣，其中30萬人已經有結果，全部是陰性。大興區所有人禁止離開北京，確實有需要離開北京的人，必須持3日內核酸檢測陰性證明。<br />\n<br />\n內地累積88557人確診，超過82400人康復出院。"},{"pid":"be51a4e55df71cd333ab8b23b01140b22eb482b9","tid":2372730,"uid":128014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我国边有疫情啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5dccd8a661259882c15d2c1de2aad83dd0ff2a83","tid":2372730,"uid":356101,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be51a4e55df71cd333ab8b23b01140b22eb482b9","tid":2372730,"uid":128014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我国边有疫情啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:38:31.000Z","msg":"你班友真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img